<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT45">
<l>purintu malariṭṭup puṇṭarikap pātam</l>
<l>parintu paṭukāṭu niṟpa terinteṅkun</l>
<l>tāṉōṅki niṟkiṉṟāṉ taṇṇaruvi vēṅkaṭamē</l>
<l>vāṉōrkku maṇṇōrkkum vaippu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Vēṅkaṭam with cool waterfalls—</l>
<l rend="indent">of [the Lord] who stands tall, being perceived everywhere,</l>
<l rend="indent">as one desiringly places flowers at the lotus feet</l>
<l rend="indent">and affectionately stays as felled trees do</l>
<l>—is the treasure for the celestials and the terrestrials.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
